# elizaos-plugins/registry Daily Update (Dec 29, 2025)
## OVERVIEW 
The day saw a new pull request to add the `plugin-coinrailz` to the registry. Discussions continued on an active issue regarding snapshot eligibility and Tangem wallet connection, with community members offering solutions and advice.

## KEY TECHNICAL DEVELOPMENTS
No new technical developments were completed today.

## NEWLY OPENED PULL REQUESTS
A new pull request, [#245](https://github.com/elizaos-plugins/registry/pull/245), was opened to add the `plugin-coinrailz` to the registry.

## CLOSED ISSUES
No issues were closed today.

## NEW ISSUES
No new issues were reported today.

## ACTIVE ISSUES
### Snapshot Eligibility and Wallet Connection Support
Discussion continued on [#6211](https://github.com/elizaos-plugins/registry/issues/6211) regarding issues with AI16Z â†’ ElizaOS migration, specifically concerning snapshot eligibility and Tangem wallet connection. A community member, om1d-sa, provided two potential solutions:
1.  Importing a cold wallet's seed phrase into a hot wallet like Phantom to perform the migration.
2.  Joining the official Discord server and using the ticket system for manual migration, verifying support staff by their ElizaLabz blue tag.
This advice was given in response to an earlier query about the issue's resolution.
